      "review_summary": "The PR changes cron local-provider preflight to build credential-bearing headers through shared provider auth helpers, passes agent/workspace directories into auth lookup, redacts preflight errors, and expands tests.\n\nPR surface: Source +83, Tests +1035. Total +1118 across 3 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. from source: current main sends no configured headers during cron provider preflight, and the PR head still omits provider-level/request headers that normal execution can send. I did not run a live local-provider reproduction in this read-only review.",
